    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/a5147bfbedb2fbe9b0a62530af1c32f2.avif?t=1758043035\" width=620 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/d9dc38a190bb5b06ba9b26124bd90e22.poster.avif?t=1758043035\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/d9dc38a190bb5b06ba9b26124bd90e22.webm?t=1758043035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/d9dc38a190bb5b06ba9b26124bd90e22.mp4?t=1758043035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massive battles everywhere: space, atmospheres, ground, water, underwater.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spaceship dogfights, on-foot combat, boarding enemy cruisers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thousands of units — from agile fighters to colossal warships.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimized for smooth gameplay even on low-end PCs and SteamDeck. <br>​</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/3429d5f95c6738f614e80179507a82c0.avif?t=1758043035\" width=620 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/21211794a44b2db5182f01acbe657dac.poster.avif?t=1758043035\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/21211794a44b2db5182f01acbe657dac.webm?t=1758043035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/21211794a44b2db5182f01acbe657dac.mp4?t=1758043035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo, with friends, or join any players you find in hubs or chat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single server for all players and groups of any size. <br>​</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/06c476b5a81e87680e83dd258a44d54d.avif?t=1758043035\" width=620 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/28adb0515ef3947522918e10e53f3ae1.poster.avif?t=1758043035\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/28adb0515ef3947522918e10e53f3ae1.webm?t=1758043035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248010/extras/28adb0515ef3947522918e10e53f3ae1.mp4?t=1758043035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Huge spherical planets up to 1000km radius with varied biomes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamless landing on planet surfaces and space stations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ship interiors, ships inside ships, free spacewalks anywhere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interplanetary flights with full ship control and unlimited speeds.</p></li></ul>",
